General.Name: John Mattson Fastighetsforetagen AB
General.Description: John Mattson Fastighetsföretagen AB (publ) operates as a residential property owner in Sweden. It owns, develops, and manages approximately 4,400 rental apartments, as well as commercial premises and leasehold properties. The company was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Lidingö, Sweden.
